Launch Checklist

Understand the publishing process
Understand google play policies
Test for core app quality
Determine content rating
Determine country distribution
Confirm overall size
Confirm platform and screen ranges
Decide free or priced
Use in-app billing
Set prices for your products
Start localization
Prepare promotional graphics, screenshots, and videos
Build the release-ready apk
Plan a beta release
Complete the store listing
Use google play badges and links
Final checks and publishing
Support users after launch


Additional Sources
https://developer.android.com/distribute/best-practices/launch/launch-checklist.html
